documentation:
Decorator, used to register a tag-class pair to this lookup object

Usage:
    @tag_lookup_object("tagname")
    class SomeClass(XmlNode):
        ...

Generate a parser which maps

Example:

```
# For <ATag ... /> nodes:
@parser.tag('ATag')
class ATagClass:
    ...

# For <DontCare classid='SomeClass' ... /> nodes:
@parser.classid('SomeClassId')
class SomeClassIdClass:
    ...
```
